1. Project Goal
Build a low-fidelity wireframe in Figma (plus optional high-fidelity mockup) for a coworking workspace platform.
The wireframe must show:

Clear navigation

All MVP pages

Logical user flow for both Coworkers and Owners


2. MVP Required Pages
Landing Page

Sign Up Page

Login Page

Owner Dashboard

Add Property Page

Add Workspace Page

My Properties Page

List of Workspaces (Search Results)

Workspace Details Page


